snippet.title: Omega Strikers - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Omega Strikers is coming to Nintendo Switch on April 27, 2023: Pre-order this free-to-play game today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/omega-strikers-switch/

Smash opponents off the arena and score goals in this lightning-fast 3v3 footbrawler. Sling slimes, toss tofu, and rocket boost to victory as one of 15+ stylish Strikers.

#OmegaStrikers #NintendoSwitch #NintendoDirect

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot
